==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Fasciole
<hw>Fas"ci*ole</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[L.
<ets>fasciola</ets> a little bandage. See <er>Fascia</er>.]</ety>
<fld>(Zool.)</fld> <def>A band of minute tubercles, bearing modified
spines, on the shells of spatangoid sea urchins. See
<er>Spatangoidea</er>.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>fascism</ent>⟦br⟧
